        <li><strong>Changes to Privacy Policy:</strong></li>
    </ol>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the &quot;Effective Date&quot; 
        will be updated accordingly. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.</p>
    <ol start="9">
        <li><strong>Contact Us:</strong></li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy Policy, please contact us at flavorsomedelights@gmail.com.<br />
        By using our website, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms. Thank you for visiting
